{"tid":1939685,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】美國醫療劇劇組捐物資幫助前線醫護人員","createTime":"2020-03-23T09:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T09:27:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a53cc757b8184ce50d350f593132ea4ffb6b8cc2","tid":1939685,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:27:13.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎在美國疫情日趨嚴重，確診數字不但急劇上升，多位荷李活藝人亦不幸感染病毒，就連當地的醫療和防疫物資都嚴重短缺。美國多部醫療劇早前就宣佈捐出拍攝用的醫療物資，幫助醫院及前線的醫護人員，當中包括美國廣播公司的《醫人當自強》（Grey's Anatomy）、《Station 19》和《好醫生》（The Good Doctor），其中《Station 19》就捐出300個N95口罩給消防局，而《醫》劇就捐出保護衣及手套。<br />\n、<br />\n此外，《紐約萬花筒》（Pose）、《芝加哥醫情》（Chicago Med）、《芝加哥烈火群英》（Chicago Fire）和《芝加哥警署》（Chicago P.D.）等劇集亦加入捐助行列，《紐》劇製作人前日就表示已捐出物資到一間醫院。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200322/large/1584880089_5723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200322%2Flarge%2F1584880089_5723.jpg&h=be5fdd02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200323/6QTA5KPE5LCN7WXHGBYZ5MWU3A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200323%2F6QTA5KPE5LCN7WXHGBYZ5MWU3A%2F&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr7YQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=c68b5711\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200323%2F6QTA5KPE5LCN7WXHGBYZ5MWU3A%2F&h=5b2735ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200323/6QTA5KPE5LCN7WXHGBYZ5MWU3A/</a>"}]}